<h1 style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:24px;font-weight:bold;color:#111827;">Subscription Paused</h1>
<p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">
  Your subscription has been paused after <strong>{{attempts}} failed payment attempt{{#unless singleAttempt}}s{{/unless}}</strong>.
</p>
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin:0 0 24px;background-color:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fca5a5;border-radius:6px;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
      <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#991b1b;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px;">Subscription ID</p>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#374151;font-family:monospace;">{{subscriptionId}}</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;">
  Please review your payment details and resume the subscription when ready.
</p>
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
  <tr>
    <td style="border-radius:6px;background-color:#1a56db;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;">Manage Subscription</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
